175 A.3d 165 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. RONALD LONG, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-339 September Term 2017

078976 November 17, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

*315A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003798-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
